      "settings": {
        "heading": "Travel Organizers",
        "text": "<p>As traveling crafters ourselves, we know how important it is to be able to travel easily with your craft supplies. You'll find that a majority of our products are designed to work in your craft room and on the road too. Please visit our \"Hints and Tips!\" page to view travel organizers grouped by the type of products they will hold.<\/p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": "",
