            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "EZ2Organize Buddy Bag Line ",
            "text": "<p>The EZ2Organize Buddy Bag Line is great for packing up little things like glitter glue, stamps, washi tape, ink pads, adhesive runners, baker's twine, re-inkers...the list is almost endless.<\/p><p>There are currently 14 Buddy Bag Designs, so you're sure to find the perfect bag for your supplies.  Please visit our \"Hints and Tips\" page to look for organizers by type of product you want to organize for travel - glitter glues, ink pads, rulers, markers...etc.<\/p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/EZ2Organize-Buddy-Bags-Craft-Supply-Organizers-by-Totally-Tiffany.jpg"
          }
        },
        "1aa23087-fc92-45d6-b877-ad0c6878aad1": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Portable tool storage",
            "text": "<p>The Ditto bag is one of our most popular items because it is so easy to use at home and when you travel. This bag will help you organize everything from tape runners to embossing folders. There's even a secret pocket for your small paper trimmer.<\/p><p>The Ditto bag will open up across your workspace for easy access to your tools and supplies, but folds in half to carry to event or just to put it away on your shelf.<\/p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/SDTT45BLK-Ditto-Tool-Bag-loaded-6_908c6b01-9176-4b18-8cef-427013a9bb4a.jpg"
          }
        },
        "5a597e89-52f4-417d-8f3e-a2a19add93e8": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "The perfect travel tote",
            "text": "<p>Lois is a versatile travel tote designed with paper crafting supplies in mind. Available in all clear vinyl and in your favorite Totally-Tiffany colors too!<\/p><p>Lois can carry 12x12 Paper Handlers, Punch and Supply Packs, Rotating Design Boards and more than a dozen buddy bags.<\/p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CLR_PNK_Pink_Lois_2.0_Loaded_with_12x12_Fab-File_XL31-ff-2.jpg"
          }
        }
      },
