      "type": "text-header",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Lois and the Ditto - a well-organized team",
        "text": "<p>Want to be able to carry your Ditto bag over your shoulder? Lois is your girl!  A fully loaded Ditto Bag will fit perfectly into our Lois Tote.<\/p><p>I live in the Pacific Northwest where rain is a common occurrence.  I use my Lois tote like a rain jacket for my Ditto bag.<\/p><p>Both the Ditto Tool Tote and the Lois Tote are part of the EZ2Organize product line.<\/p>",
